to remain silent.

784
00:52:46.573 --> 00:52:50.211
Hey. I'm just saying.
Just saying.

785
00:52:53.312 --> 00:52:57.218
In the end. does all that
smarts really pay off?

786
00:52:58.484 --> 00:53:03.021
