788
00:53:05.456 --> 00:53:07.491
Well. not funny.

789
00:53:07.492 --> 00:53:10.764
I have this theory
about smarts...

790
00:53:12.931 --> 00:53:15.234
That it gets in the way
of seeing things.

791
00:53:17.001 --> 00:53:20.907
