have to have her.

801
00:54:13.357 --> 00:54:15.394
She brings that out
in a man.

802
00:54:19.029 --> 00:54:20.265
Let me guess.

803
00:54:22.299 --> 00:54:23.968
I kill him.

804
00:54:33.242 --> 00:54:35.880
See? Those smarts again.

805
00:54:37.681 --> 00:54:41.219
