00:56:53.312 --> 00:56:57.284
and Carl has just enough left in him
to put a bullet between his eyes.

838
00:57:00.319 --> 00:57:02.356
What did I say
about improvising?

839
00:57:04.091 --> 00:57:05.993
Where is he?
I want to see him.

