846
00:57:48.233 --> 00:57:50.701
Cold as they come.

847
00:57:50.702 --> 00:57:52.338
Why didn't he know you?

848
00:57:57.477 --> 00:58:00.810
No. Let me.

849
00:58:00.811 --> 00:58:03.081
You sure. babe?

850
00:58:03.848 --> 00:58:06.284
