929
01:04:08.606 --> 01:04:10.739
until he
and the mother died.

930
01:04:10.740 --> 01:04:12.708
She always wanted me
to be provided for.

931
01:04:12.709 --> 01:04:15.212
so he agreed to put
something aside for me.

932
01:04:15.213 --> 01:04:17.947
<i>She cleaned out the trust
three days ago.</i>

933
01:04:20.983 --> 01:04:25.486
